Here’s a small collection of KiCAD symbols and footprints that teams may find useful:

github.com

GitHub - ryukoposting/FRC-KiCAD: KiCAD Symbol and Footprint libraries for FRC

KiCAD Symbol and Footprint libraries for FRC

I’ve included schematic symbols and PCB footprints for:

  • RoboRIO
  • Spark MAX
  • Talon FXS
  • Talon SRX
  • Thrifty Nova

This deprecates my previous RoboRIO-KiCAD project, which only had libraries for the RoboRIO.

These libraries make it easier to develop custom PCBs for your robot during the build season, since they eliminate a lot of the guesswork involved with connector pinouts, mounting hole dimensions, and the like.

All footprints include a 3D model of the the device they connect to, so you can see how your board will look in real life:
